{"title": "Evo", "summary": "Continuous Line Luminaire", "body": "Modular glowing stick pendant LED luminaire, made of machined frosted polymer and aluminum joiners. This simple system allows for modules to be added as desired to form a continuous homogeneous lit line. Simply powered by a suspension cable for a clean look.\n\n*2019*\n\n\n\n[lp=Ringo-Studio-Modern-Age-Studio-NYC (1).jpg]\n*Modern Age NY*\n\n\n\n\n**&&Components&&**\n[lp=Frici Evo Parts.jpg]\nThe fixture is easily assembled to form a continuous run of light. The sections are joined end to end and held in place with only two screws on the top and the current flows through them by using compact spring loaded connectors.\n\n\n[lp=P93M-ASSEMBLY.jpg]\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n**&&Development&&**\n\n\n[lp=EVO Sketch.jpg]\n[lp=PXL_20220207_145816156.jpg]\n\n\n\n\n**&&Final Product&&**\n\n\n[lp=P93M EVO SCENE 2.jpg]\n\n\n[lp=Government of Canada Office Site 1.jpg]\n*Government of Canada Offices*\n\n[lp=Government of Canada Office Site 2.jpg]\n*Government of Canada Offices*\n\n[lp=P93M Frici Evo Cover.jpg]\n\nIn addition to these pictures, this product has been used as decorative lighting in the offices of Google, Microsoft and other large projects.", "image": "Ringo-Studio-Modern-Age-Studio-NYC Cover.jpg", "id": 19}